Project subject - and used languages
------------------------------------
Langueage Detection For Turkish, English, German.

Brief about project content
----------------------------
This program determines the language of the given text. But there is a restriction for the number of languages. Inputs can be in Turkish, English, German or mixed up.The output of the program prints the detected language and the probabilities of each 3 languages.

Prerequirement
--------------
Before running the program be sure that the traning set named "data" folder is in the same directory with lang_detector.py

Compile & Run
-------------
python3 lang_detector.py <input_text>

Input format
------------
Program takes input string from console. ( As shown in Compile & Run section )

Output format
-------------
Program prints result to the console screen.

Example Usage
-------------
$ python3 lang_detector.py "bu proje incredible"

Given string is in Turkish language.

Probability Details
----------------------------------------------------
Turkish : 99.96 %
German : 0.04 %
English : 0.01 %

Total Time: 6.37 seconds